  "text": "I'm a little confused. I have partially understood, but I'm not sure that I'm fully understood. Can I restate that another way? I can restate that in many ways, given this instruments, a knowledge of your laboratory sound complexes. I will strive for a shorter distortion at this time. Two kinds there are who can deal with those such as yourself, who having a vape innate distortion towards knowledge, giving of the thewe of one can heal, but do not. And those who having the same knowledge, but showing no significant distortion consciously towards the law of one in mind, body, or spirit, yet and nevertheless have opened a channel to the same ability. The point being that there are those who, without proper training, shall we say. Nevertheless, here it is a further item of interest that those whose life does not equal their work may find some difficulty in absorbing the energy of intelligent infinity and thus become quite distorted in such a way as to cause disharmony in themselves and others and perhaps even find it necessary to cease with the healing activity. Those who seek to serve and are willing to be trained in thought, word, and action are those who will be able to comfortably maintain and be distorted towards service in the area of feeling.",
